WEBVTT

00:07:59.417 --> 00:08:01.684
we asked the district
administration officials

00:08:01.708 --> 00:08:03.309
to speak to Anitha's parents,

00:08:03.333 --> 00:08:04.601
and it worked.

00:08:04.625 --> 00:08:07.684
And then there is Padma.

00:08:07.708 --> 00:08:09.976
Padma and I went to college together.

00:08:10.000 --> 00:08:13.750
She's the first in her entire village
to attend graduation.

00:08:14.458 --> 00:08:17.059
She had been working with me at Bodhi Tree

00:08:17.083 --> 00:08:20.518
until one day she decides
to go to graduate school.

00:08:20.542 --> 00:08:22.434
I asked her why.

00:08:22.458 --> 00:08:24.934
She told me that she wanted to make sure

00:08:24.958 --> 00:08:28.893
that she would never be
a liability or a burden to anyone

00:08:28.917 --> 00:08:30.667
at any point in her life.